273
00:14:10.683 --> 00:14:14.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but we can't spotlight residents
who don't follow the rules.

274
00:14:14.186 --> 00:14:16.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
