378
00:20:01.033 --> 00:20:03.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
that is what's happening here, right?

379
00:20:06.371 --> 00:20:09.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
