of how my yurt exploded?

422
00:22:05.574 --> 00:22:09.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No, you always get so frustrated
by your own interruptions, you give up.

423
00:22:09.953 --> 00:22:14.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It was President's Day,
and the humidity was...

424
00:22:14.708 --> 00:22:17.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
