426
00:22:19.087 --> 00:22:20.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Portia.

427
00:22:20.088 --> 00:22:23.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, my God.
