431
00:22:32.309 --> 00:22:35.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, of course it is. There's a rule
for everything in this damn place.

432
00:22:35.437 --> 00:22:39.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
