where it demands to be born.

433
00:22:39.858 --> 00:22:44.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you know they will not let us
run Vybrant in our apartment?

434
00:22:44.404 --> 00:22:46.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Are we still doing that?

435
